1411
01:25:50,200 --> 01:25:52,970
She was defrauded out of every penny
she owns and then some.

1412
01:25:53,040 --> 01:25:56,170
And I know you're out of there,
but I figured you'd know.

1413
01:25:56,240 --> 01:25:59,700
Yeah, sure, I do know.
I, I, I...

1414
01:26:12,590 --> 01:26:15,720
<i>[Ray]
I came as soon as I heard.</i>

1415
01:26:17,130 --> 01:26:20,020
I got exactly what I deserved.

1416
01:26:20,150 --> 01:26:22,680
I really missed you, Frenchy.

1417
01:26:22,750 --> 01:26:25,880
<i>I'm sorry I blew
our cookie company,</i>

1418
01:26:25,960 --> 01:26:29,250
<i>but I'm even more sorry
I blew our marriage, Ray.</i>

1419
01:26:29,330 --> 01:26:32,820
What do you do? Everybody makes
mistakes, you know what I mean?

1420
01:26:32,900 --> 01:26:35,590
The important thing is
I still love you.

1421
01:26:35,670 --> 01:26:38,360
I don't deserve it.
I behaved badly.

1422
01:26:38,430 --> 01:26:42,270
You behaved like an ass, but that's one
of those "A" words you used to practice.

1423
01:26:42,340 --> 01:26:43,900
Ass.

1424
01:26:43,970 --> 01:26:48,540
But I'm not the easiest guy to
get along with. I'm not Mr. Sensitive.

1425
01:26:48,610 --> 01:26:52,740
There's a lot of things
I could've done differently, maybe.

1426
01:26:52,820 --> 01:26:57,120
