1432
01:27:13,270 --> 01:27:16,170
- You still want me?
- Still want you? I'm...

1433
01:27:16,240 --> 01:27:19,500
Frenchy, you gotta ask a question
like that? I'm crazy about you.

1434
01:27:19,580 --> 01:27:21,510
I'm crazy about you too.

1435
01:27:21,580 --> 01:27:23,670
You're a goddess to me.
I'm nuts for you.

1436
01:27:23,750 --> 01:27:25,810
You got...
Of course I want you.

1437
01:27:25,880 --> 01:27:28,080
But we're broke, you know.
We haven't got a dime.

1438
01:27:28,150 --> 01:27:31,310
We don't even own a stick
of this furniture we're sittin' on.

1439
01:27:31,390 --> 01:27:34,650
Can I show you something? Will you
sit here? May I show you one thing?

1440
01:27:34,720 --> 01:27:37,190
