- Okay.

1441
01:27:39,630 --> 01:27:42,150
I think you're gonna be
very, very proud of me.

1442
01:27:42,230 --> 01:27:44,170
<i>What?</i>

1443
01:27:44,230 --> 01:27:49,300
<i>- That's Chi Chi Potter's.
- Was. Was Chi Chi... Was.</i>

1444
01:27:49,370 --> 01:27:53,100
Keyword. Was. I'm tellin' you,
I never felt so great.

1445
01:27:53,180 --> 01:27:56,080
I was back in action again.
I felt alive, you know.

