1458
01:28:34,280 --> 01:28:37,310
It's good to see you got
the same great instincts.

1459
01:28:37,390 --> 01:28:39,980
- You're so wrong.
- It really is.

1460
01:28:40,060 --> 01:28:43,550
- You take all those lessons, you think you got taste.
- Wait a minute.

1461
01:28:43,630 --> 01:28:45,590
I'm gonna show you something.

1462
01:28:45,660 --> 01:28:49,830
You think you learn class and taste,
but you know nothing about jewelry.

1463
01:28:49,900 --> 01:28:53,840
We take this and fence it.
